title: Tommi Stumpff Collection (Industrial/EBM)
description:
This is a collection of Tommi Stumpff releases. Tommi Stumpff was a pioneer in the early 80s EBM scene. In some regards, he was way ahead of his time.

If you like Industrial, EBM, Electropunk, or Minimal music, check Tommi Stumpff out.
